Title: Korea's AI workforce lags behind China, Japan
Description: Korea is lagging far behind China and Japan in competitiveness of the artificial intelligence (AI) workforce, as weak local research infrastructure is causing an outflow of AI experts here, a Seoul-based research institute said Sunday. According to a survey on 30 AI experts here, Korea's AI manpower competitiveness index came in at 5.2 on a 10-point scale. By placing the index of the United States at 10, China scored 8.1 points in the figure. Japan also edged out Korea with six points, according to the survey by Korea Economic Research Institute.
